         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">26 Augst [18]84 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ With reference to your letter of the 20th instant, ¶  I now beg to inform you that the Chief Secretary has approved of Mr Gerhard Renner being engaged as Junior Assistant in...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">84.08.26</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Thomas Wilson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 3017, p. 441, unit 68, VPRS 1187/P, outward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">26 Augst [18]84</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With reference to your letter of the 20th instant,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to G. Berry, 20 August 1884.</p>
               </note> I now beg to inform you that the Chief Secretary has approved of Mr Gerhard Renner being engaged as Junior Assistant in your Department at the rate of 7/6 (seven shillings &amp; sixpence) per diem, vice Mr Leon Henry resigned, and to request you will be good enough to inform me of the date on which Mr Gerhard Renner entered upon his duties.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-family: Geneva; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to T. Wilson, 27 August 1884.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your most obedient servant,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>T. R. Wilson</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">The Government Botanist</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c<space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">Arnold St</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Geneva; "
               xml:lang="en">South Yarra</p>
         </div>
